config SCADA_KUNIT_TEST
	tristate "0xSCADA KUnit tests" if !KUNIT_ALL_TESTS
	depends on KUNIT
	depends on CRYPTO
	depends on CRYPTO_SHA256
	default KUNIT_ALL_TESTS
	help
	  KUnit tests for kernel functionality critical to 0xSCADA
	  industrial applications, including:
	  - Cryptographic hash verification (SHA256)
	  - Timer precision and monotonicity
	  - Memory allocation reliability

	  If unsure, say N.
